org.glassfish.admin.amx.base

Interface Utility

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BulkAccess, Ext, Pathnames, Query, Realms, RuntimeRoot, SystemInfo, Tools

    @Taxonomy(stability=UNCOMMITTED)
public interface Utility
    Marker interface which indicates that this MBean is a utility object. Utilities objects are usually singletons, but are not required to be so.
